race.comment: Several of these close to wins. ETCHED IN BLUE (5) is heading in the right direction finishing third fresh then second last time. Fitter again and the extra trip a plus. Expected to go close again. OCTANE REIGN (6) turned in a much better effort last time when stepping up to a similar journey. Raced on pace and fought on well for third. Can give a sight again. PANELLI (7) sat handy fresh and fought on well for fifth. Fitter and can give a sight again.  PUNIC WAR (8) is an eight-start maiden who looks close to a win after a narrow defeat last time over 1450m at Tatura, finishing third. Will roll forward over the extra ground ike last couple of starts and give a sight. Nearing a win and looks a big chance to break through.
